com.stormpath.sdk.idsite

Class IDSiteException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.stormpath.sdk.idsite.IDSiteException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Error, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IDSiteSessionTimeoutException, InvalidIDSiteTokenException

    public abstract class IDSiteException
extends Exception
implements Error
    An abstract checked exception denoting an error in IDSite.

    This is a generic Exception that specific IDSite exception implementations representing an actual ID Site error can extend.

    Since:
    1.0.RC5
    See Also:
    InvalidIDSiteTokenException, IDSiteSessionTimeoutException, Serialized Form
